data.meta_description:
22 likes, 6 comments - hoborlando on October 26, 2023: "🎤 TONIGHT • ANDRÉS CALAMARO 🎤 Head over to 🔗 livemu.sc/3Sfi4rx NOW to get last minute tickets 🎫 Additional show information below!

➡️ RESTAURANT & BAR: Pre-show fuel?! We got you! 🍔🍻 Grab a bite to eat and some delicious cocktails before the show at our Restaurant & Bar! To view the menu & make reservations, visit 🔗 bit.ly/3mzhfZo
➡️ BAG POLICY: If you're bringing a bag, please make sure it adheres to our new bag policy: Bags shall not exceed 12” x 6” x 12” (30cm x 15cm x 30cm). Backpacks and other multi-compartment bags or laptop cases are prohibited regardless of size.
➡️ MOBILE TICKETS: Your phone is your ticket. Add tickets to your wallet or transfer tickets to friends before reaching the music hall!
➡️ FAQ: For all venue questions please visit our website 🔗 bit.ly/3OUgRkA".
